1
00:00:14,725 --> 00:00:18,487
♪Allergic to fast-food love,
even if it's too naive♪

2
00:00:18,562 --> 00:00:22,162
♪Just like a hug needs
the right body heat♪

3
00:00:22,287 --> 00:00:25,437
♪Your “same here” carries
a touch of resolve♪

4
00:00:25,862 --> 00:00:29,412
♪Pack my bags,
we can set off right now♪

5
00:00:29,637 --> 00:00:33,112
♪The future is a wondrous,
unknown adventure♪

6
00:00:33,250 --> 00:00:36,712
♪The journey itself is what truly matters
before the destination♪

7
00:00:36,787 --> 00:00:40,975
♪Those moments together
are what bind us strongest♪

8
00:00:41,025 --> 00:00:42,612
♪Connect♪

9
00:00:42,625 --> 00:00:43,275
♪Let's go!♪

10
00:00:43,612 --> 00:00:47,137
♪Leave worries behind
in yesterday's sentimentality♪

11
00:00:47,237 --> 00:00:50,675
♪Today, no dwelling on
negative emotions♪

12
00:00:50,750 --> 00:00:53,450
♪Tomorrow holds more luck♪

13
00:00:53,450 --> 00:00:55,262
♪Together we'll create moving melodies♪

14
00:00:55,262 --> 00:00:58,199
♪The future begins to take shape♪

15
00:00:59,075 --> 00:01:02,375
=Love in A Secret=
(I Just Want to Drown With You)

16
00:01:02,675 --> 00:01:06,262
=Episode 19=

17
00:01:11,600 --> 00:01:13,320
Don't you have anything to say to me?

18
00:01:16,240 --> 00:01:17,220
I'm going to the hospital

19
00:01:18,440 --> 00:01:20,080
and let Mr. Lu rest.

20
00:01:20,800 --> 00:01:21,800
You should sleep early.

21
00:01:25,720 --> 00:01:27,680
You think I'm unreasonable?

22
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:32,240
I just wanted to be a little braver.

23
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:35,720
What have I done wrong?

24
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:38,720
Some things

25
00:01:39,720 --> 00:01:41,120
are more important than love.

26
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:43,240
But some people say

27
00:01:45,720 --> 00:01:48,200
love is fearless.

28
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:59,200
You approached me first.

29
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:10,080
Lu.

30
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:39,080
Lu.

31
00:02:41,640 --> 00:02:42,800
We can't do this.

32
00:02:59,888 --> 00:03:01,640
(It isn't just you falling.)

33
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:02,840
(It's us.)

34
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:05,760
(If the end of the abyss)

35
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:08,640
(requires you to bear the pain,)

36
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:12,840
(then let me be the villain instead.)

37
00:03:21,480 --> 00:03:22,760
Hello, Zhu.

38
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:25,840
We've picked up
another bit of gossip about your family.

39
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:27,640
Luckily, I shut it down in time.

40
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:29,000
It's news about your brother

41
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:31,000
getting engaged to a girl surnamed Fan.

42
00:03:52,440 --> 00:03:54,440
Hello, Zhu?

43
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:03,280
Hello?

44
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:39,960
(Makeup brushes must be aired by the
windows every Thursday for two hours.)

45
00:04:39,960 --> 00:04:41,720
(Check the air conditioner before bed.)

46
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:44,000
(Set a timer.
Don't leave it on all night.)

47
00:04:49,520 --> 00:04:52,520
(Put the milk back on the third shelf
of the fridge.)

48
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:55,680
(The dark blue hoodie
must be washed in cold water.)

49
00:04:57,960 --> 00:05:00,840
(Cooling temperature not lower
than 26 degree Celcius.)

50
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:06,200
(Put the phone on the charging dock
before bed.)

51
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:08,280
(Set the alarm ten minutes earlier.)

52
00:05:08,280 --> 00:05:10,480
(Qin is my best friend in college.)

53
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:17,440
(Chen Tianze is my childhood friend.)

54
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:29,720
(I love you)

55
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:32,040
(like I love myself.)

56
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,040
Zhu,

57
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,400
you're awake.

58
00:05:50,640 --> 00:05:51,960
Why am I in the hospital?

59
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:53,960
You called me.

60
00:06:03,520 --> 00:06:04,440
Ze,

61
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:06,720
thank you.

62
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,280
Zhu,

63
00:06:09,280 --> 00:06:12,000
do you know what condition
you're in right now?

64
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,640
You know already?

65
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:16,480
Why didn't you tell Mr. Lu?

66
00:06:19,640 --> 00:06:21,400
What difference would it make?

67
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:24,520
It's okay, Ze.

68
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:26,360
Don't worry.

69
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:29,720
I might not die.

70
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:37,320
(If it were you,)

71
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:40,160
(what kind of ending would you want?)

72
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:44,800
Ze,

73
00:06:46,200 --> 00:06:47,560
what kind of person is Zhu

74
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:50,360
to you?

75
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:55,280
When I first came back and saw you,

76
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:57,040
I felt you'd changed a lot.

77
00:06:58,040 --> 00:07:00,600
But I couldn't quite say how.

78
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:03,680
You used to be gentle and kind,

79
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:05,560
as if nothing weighed on you.

80
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:08,040
You were like a cloud in the sky

81
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:09,240
that's impossible to hold onto.

82
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:14,160
But now, you're harder to read.

83
00:07:15,080 --> 00:07:16,280
Zhu,

84
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:18,000
you weren't like this before.

85
00:07:18,520 --> 00:07:20,120
At least you cherished yourself before.

86
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,520
Alright, Ze.

87
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:26,680
How am I not cherishing myself?

88
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:29,400
Am I not lying in the hospital
being treated?

89
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:32,440
Fine.

90
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:35,400
I just think as long as you're here,
that's enough.

91
00:07:35,640 --> 00:07:37,560
You have to cooperate with treatment.

92
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:40,480
I promise.

93
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,160
Ze,

94
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:52,200
did you know Ye Man
is going to announce his engagement?

95
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:55,360
I know.

96
00:07:55,840 --> 00:07:57,360
Can you do me a favor?

97
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:12,680
What's wrong?

98
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,840
I don't know whether
what I'm doing is right.

99
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:22,240
None of your decisions has been wrong.

100
00:08:24,440 --> 00:08:25,800
But I've dragged you into this.

101
00:08:27,440 --> 00:08:28,600
That's nothing.

102
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,240
Being able to help you

103
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,240
makes me happy.

104
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:35,600
But if we do, Lu...

105
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:40,680
Miss Lu will return to her original
life path.

106
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:42,520
She'll meet many new people.

107
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:43,960
She's just a young girl.

108
00:08:44,280 --> 00:08:45,400
She'll forget you soon

109
00:08:45,680 --> 00:08:46,800
and everything that happened.

110
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:54,240
And you,

111
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,120
Man,

112
00:08:58,920 --> 00:09:01,000
the debts you need to repay
for your dad

113
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,520
and the injustices you need to clear,

114
00:09:02,520 --> 00:09:03,920
all of it can finally come to light.

115
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,280
I know you love her.

116
00:09:08,800 --> 00:09:10,590
But you'll just have to
endure a little more.

117
00:09:16,637 --> 00:09:17,557
So,

118
00:09:17,612 --> 00:09:20,052
do you still need me
to interrupt the press conference

119
00:09:20,837 --> 00:09:22,560
and tell everyone how you feel for him?

120
00:09:23,920 --> 00:09:24,760
But

121
00:09:26,625 --> 00:09:30,025
isn't love supposed to be fearless?

122
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:33,280
What if it wasn't that much love
to begin with?

123
00:09:34,487 --> 00:09:41,325
♪Yet somehow we never said
that some people are only passerby♪

124
00:09:42,020 --> 00:09:48,800
♪I've seen how romantic you are♪

125
00:09:49,725 --> 00:09:55,450
♪So I could easily foresee
the fierce heartbreak♪

126
00:09:55,640 --> 00:09:57,080
(Evening News.)

127
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:57,920
(Today,)

128
00:09:57,920 --> 00:10:00,040
(the newly appointed young heir
of Lu Group announced)

129
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:02,800
(his engagement to
his Standard-educated girlfriend.)

130
00:10:02,800 --> 00:10:05,320
(Recent rumors of an improper
relationship with his stepsister)

131
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:06,360
(have been dispelled.)

132
00:10:10,512 --> 00:10:17,980
♪What happened to us? From entangled
with each other to having nothing to say♪

133
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:25,980
♪Regret found its place
after repeated disappointments♪

134
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:33,380
♪Who was just a passerby
doesn't matter anymore♪

135
00:10:33,380 --> 00:10:43,500
♪There's no need to argue over
who was the one more loved♪

136
00:11:03,280 --> 00:11:05,320
Do you see these bottles?

137
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:08,800
I'm like them.

138
00:11:12,920 --> 00:11:14,800
Something that can be discarded
at any time.

139
00:11:19,040 --> 00:11:20,400
Since I was little,

140
00:11:21,880 --> 00:11:22,760
my mom

141
00:11:24,800 --> 00:11:25,800
and dad

142
00:11:27,520 --> 00:11:30,160
treated me like a bargaining chip
to threaten each other.

143
00:11:31,280 --> 00:11:32,887
Only my sister and you

144
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:35,112
loved me briefly,

145
00:11:35,520 --> 00:11:37,200
but with all your hearts.

146
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:40,800
And now,

147
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:44,440
you're leaving too.

148
00:11:46,275 --> 00:11:47,875
In this world,

149
00:11:47,925 --> 00:11:50,285
no one even knows who I am.

150
00:11:52,880 --> 00:11:54,120
I have a secret.

151
00:11:55,280 --> 00:11:56,560
Do you want to hear it?

152
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:03,200
From the first time I met you,

153
00:12:04,880 --> 00:12:06,080
I knew

154
00:12:07,720 --> 00:12:10,480
you weren't the same
as the Lu family's daughter.

155
00:12:11,640 --> 00:12:13,040
She likes blue.

156
00:12:13,800 --> 00:12:15,200
You like red.

157
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:18,840
She paints in warm tones.

158
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:21,280
You prefer cool tones.

159
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:25,320
She likes lilies.

160
00:12:27,280 --> 00:12:28,960
You like irises.

161
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:32,560
You're not the same.

162
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:35,240
Not at all.

163
00:12:42,840 --> 00:12:44,760
That's when I started investigating you.

164
00:12:46,500 --> 00:12:48,720
But since you had your reasons
for hiding your identity,

165
00:12:50,487 --> 00:12:53,062
I didn't want to tear open your scars.

166
00:12:55,712 --> 00:12:56,537
Sun,

167
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:04,080
whether you're Zhu or Sun,

168
00:13:06,520 --> 00:13:07,560
I will

169
00:13:10,787 --> 00:13:13,267
protect you

170
00:13:15,440 --> 00:13:17,280
as a brother.

171
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:19,440
Okay?

172
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:22,275
Does it have to be

173
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:28,720
only as a brother?

174
00:13:34,512 --> 00:13:39,012
♪Bit by bit, I'll forget you♪

175
00:13:39,237 --> 00:13:43,025
♪Bit by bit, I'll erase the memories♪

176
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:47,275
♪From now on,
your image won't linger in my mind♪

177
00:13:47,275 --> 00:13:51,412
♪Nor will those fragments of the past♪

178
00:13:51,537 --> 00:13:55,312
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

179
00:13:55,312 --> 00:13:59,087
♪I'll learn to stop longing for
what's gone♪

180
00:13:59,087 --> 00:14:01,362
♪The you in my memories♪

181
00:14:01,362 --> 00:14:03,375
♪Will fade from clarity♪

182
00:14:03,375 --> 00:14:08,812
♪How much longer must I wait to♪

183
00:14:10,375 --> 00:14:15,812
♪Forget you completely?♪
